		<tr valign=top>
			<td class="BoardRowB" colspan=2 width="83%">
				I don't see the playstyles as being non-compatible. <br>  <br> The problem with RP first is that it lends itself to X-teaming.  This server is hardcoded to prevent that, so all an Alliance between say and Good and Neutral guild would mean is Non-Aggression. <br>  <br> We have a three way war.  The Top Dawg will always be the target of the lesser powers.  Evil complains that G&amp;N attack it rather than each other?  Let me get you a handkerchief.  But if by some Miracle Good pulls ahead, I would fully expect Evil and Neutral to do the same. <br>  <br> I still say that there will be NO serious Good/Neutral Alliances.  You might see a smattering of this in some RP guilds with a set 'storyline' or theme, but it will not be a serious impact.  The fact that you CAN'T TELL a Good Human from a Neutral Human from an Evil Human will lead to distrust and conflict.
