				Ergoyan, if you want GvE go to Vallon, thats how it is now. No teams, 12 races vs 4, miss matched. The darks are pretty much dead, soon all thats left is going to be the &quot;good&quot; team on Vallon. Vallon went blue quite a few months ago. We are coming to this new server because we want war. We wanted racewar, but we were cheated out of that. Now we want a holy war. We got our hardcoded teams. If you want to RP, by all means RP, but RP in your alliance (team), and kill your enemies. This is EQ's last chance at PvP IMO. <br>  <br> Personally I think the blues will get beat off of the server in the first few weeks. You either have a stomach for PvP or you dont, and those that do already play on PvP servers. We will see.......... <br>  <br>  <br> ~Ren
