				The server is new.  The ruleset is new.  Like every other sever Verant has established, it is the code that determines the basic nature of the sever. <br>  <br> Most players will always take the easiest path to develope their character.  It is human nature to do so.  Regardless of their mindset when creating their character, the will adjust to the environment in which they must operate. <br>  <br> Therefore, the code determines the attitude and behaviour of the players.  The palyers are the nature of the server.
