			<td class="BoardRowB" colspan=2 width="83%">
				I see the server from this angle. <br>  <br> Agnostics have been slain for their lack of belief in the Gods that built Norrath. As such all persons now follow one God or another.  <br>  <br> The forces of evil are on a mission to destroy all that is good or anything that does not subscribe to their way of life. <br>  <br> The forces of Good see the forces of evil as a threat to all that is good in the world and will attack them on sight. <br>  <br> The forces of good see those that follow the Neutral gods as weak. They are just a step removed from evil for their lack of coming to the side of light therefore they too will be considered the enemy. <br>  <br> The forces of Neutrality see Good and Evil as the extremists. They seek a balance in life that can only be attained by eliminating those that stray from the center.  <br>  <br> As such I fully expect to kill all the forces of light and dark I come upon in my travels. I do not see things in black or white as they are too far removed from the balance that must be attained. <br>  <br> 
